About AMG 


AMG OverviewPhilosophyHistoryClientsProductsAMG FundsAMG Wealth PartnersAffiliatesManagement Team


AMG Overview

Affiliated Managers Group, Inc. (NYSE: AMG) is a global asset management company with equity investments in leading boutique investment management firms. For over 23 years, we have generated superior growth by partnering with the highest quality boutique investment management firms, using direct equity ownership in a framework that closely aligns our interests with those of our Affiliate partners. AMG’s strategy is to generate growth through the internal growth of existing Affiliates, as well as through investments in new Affiliates, and additional investments in existing Affiliates. While providing our Affiliates with continued operational autonomy, AMG provides centralized assistance in strategic matters, marketing, distribution, product development and operations.  As of March 31, 2017, AMG’s aggregate assets under management were approximately $754 billion in over 550 investment products across a broad range of active, return-oriented strategies for institutional and retail clients around the world.




