	FaciliCon - Total Facility Services










 








































 
                           An Industry Leader in Office Furniture Installation 
and Office Systems Technology                         
                        
FaciliCon is the largest commercial furniture installation service provider in 
the Carolinas.                         The company continues to succeed and grow 
because of our common commitment to our founding vision:                         
To be a high-quality group of operations professionals who can fully meet customer 
needs and consistently                         set the region’s service standard 
for contract furniture installation.                     
 
                        
The FaciliCon team has done their best to fulfill this vision every working day 
since the company’s                         founding in 1992. As a result, we 
enjoy opportunities to work with many of the best and most successful            
            dealers and apply our expertise to numerous corporate office 
installations as well as a broad range                         of projects in 
healthcare, financial services, retail, government, education and other sectors. 
                    
 
                        
Our primary geographic markets are the regions around Charlotte and 
Raleigh/Durham, North Carolina, and                         
Greenville/Spartanburg, South Carolina. Our warehouse locations—Durham, 
Charlotte and Greenville—offer                         ready access to 
metropolitan areas and interstate systems, enabling FaciliCon to 
cost-effectively perform                         delivery and installation 
throughout this large operating area.                     










 
